# Architecture: pic.graph → pic.reduce (scf+arith+memref) → pic.runtime → LLVM IR / SPIR-V
# 7 nodes: γ⁺ Constructor, γ⁻ Destructor, δ Duplicator, H History, L Log-Bond, ω Operation, R Reverse-Vec
# 4 reversible rules: Annihilation, Duplication, Uncomputation, Congruence
# 4 invariants: linearity of principal ports, boundary interface consistency, confluence, conservation of topological info

## 🔴 Tier 0 — Architecture (foundational correctness)

[x] C1. Replace indirect dispatch with static opcode switch
[x] C2. Formalize host-allocated arena — no malloc inside kernels
